appetites of the filthy rich

55:18.750 --> 55:20.116
are specific.

55:20.118 --> 55:23.119
Altered from that
of the common man.

55:23.121 --> 55:25.188
Do you mind?

55:26.691 --> 55:30.126
I feed some of that hunger
with this building.

55:30.128 --> 55:32.996
(clicks)

55:32.998 --> 55:35.798
My art.

55:35.800 --> 55:39.802
But sometimes,
if I really want

55:39.804 --> 55:42.739
