56:05.830 --> 56:08.031
<i> It was a perfectly designed</i>
<i> torture chamber.</i>

56:09.000 --> 56:12.001
<i> An engineered alibi.</i>

56:12.003 --> 56:14.404
<i> Secret chutes and rooms</i>

56:14.406 --> 56:16.372
<i> to hide and dispose</i>
<i> of the bodies.</i>

56:17.509 --> 56:20.410
<i> Hallways with no exits.</i>

56:20.412 --> 56:22.311
(screaming)

56:22.313 --> 56:25.815
<i> Walls were lined with asbestos</i>

56:25.817 --> 56:28.084
