57:02.420 --> 57:04.187
Help. No, please.

57:04.189 --> 57:06.055
No, help!

57:06.057 --> 57:08.024
IRIS:
<i> No one knows how many died.</i>

57:08.026 --> 57:11.227
<i> Rumor has it</i>
<i> he averaged three a week.</i>

57:11.229 --> 57:14.063
<i> A lot more if he went</i>
<i> on a bender.</i>

57:14.065 --> 57:16.065
Help!

57:16.067 --> 57:18.101
