58:11.089 --> 58:12.088
(chuckles)

58:12.090 --> 58:14.690
IRIS:
<i> His loyal minion.</i>

58:14.692 --> 58:17.026
<i> Miss Evers, the laundress.</i>

58:19.297 --> 58:22.498
<i> She said she could get a stain</i>
<i> out of anything for Mr. March</i>

58:22.500 --> 58:25.268
<i> using a secret ingredient--</i>

58:25.270 --> 58:28.171
<i> love.</i>

58:33.845 --> 58:35.411
(groans)

58:48.126 --> 58:50.193
(praying softly)

58:52.997 --> 58:55.064
My father was a true believer.

58:56.668 --> 59:00.002
Ate the little cracker
and drank the wine every Sunday.

59:00.004 --> 59:02.004
(inhales sharply)

59:02.006 --> 59:05.241
And he was the meanest
son of a bitch you've ever seen.

59:06.811 --> 59:09.912
Kill a cat for purring too loud.

59:09.914 --> 59:12.548
(clicking tongue)

59:12.550 --> 59:16.185
You want me to tell you
the worst thing in this world?

59:16.187 --> 59:18.254
Religion.

59:19.924 --> 59:22.225
That and regulations.

59:22.227 --> 59:25.661
God is in my heart so I
know there is always hope.

59:32.537 --> 59:34.670
You think there
is hope now?

59:37.208 --> 59:40.509
You think God is
going to protect you

59:40.511 --> 59:43.279
from the head
of this hammer?

59:45.516 --> 59:48.851
Or the six floors
you're about to fall?

59:48.853 --> 59:51.187
As long as there is a God,

59:51.189 --> 59:55.124
men like you can kill thousands,

59:55.126 --> 59:57.560
millions,

59:57.562 --> 1:00:00.663
but you will never find peace.

1:00:03.268 --> 1:00:06.369
(laughs)

1:00:06.371 --> 1:00:09.372
Well then,

1:00:09.374 --> 1:00:11.807
I guess I'm just going
to have to kill God.

1:00:14.045 --> 1:00:17.113
That is my message
to the world.

1:00:29.427 --> 1:00:31.060
(groans)

1:00:31.062 --> 1:00:34.297
Fly!

1:00:34.299 --> 1:00:36.499
I'll fetch you a clean shirt.

1:00:41.839 --> 1:00:43.639
And I want every Bible

1:00:43.641 --> 1:00:47.343
