<i> out in the world.</i>

1:01:38.363 --> 1:01:40.496
<i> They say somebody</i>
<i> turned him in.</i>

1:01:40.498 --> 1:01:41.864
<i> No one knows who,</i>

1:01:41.866 --> 1:01:44.633
