1:01:54.645 --> 1:01:57.580
(knocking)

1:01:59.851 --> 1:02:01.317
I'm sorry to disturb you, sir.

1:02:01.319 --> 1:02:03.652
I have some very bad news.

1:02:03.654 --> 1:02:05.421
The police are here.

1:02:29.180 --> 1:02:31.247
(sighs heavily)

1:02:58.943 --> 1:03:01.811
Oh, Miss Evers.

1:03:01.813 --> 1:03:05.381
You have always been
the only one I can count on.

1:03:05.383 --> 1:03:07.483
You are a pillar.

1:03:07.485 --> 1:03:10.052
And so I give you the honors.

1:03:11.255 --> 1:03:13.322
What order shall we die in?

1:03:14.425 --> 1:03:16.592
Oh, Mr. March.

1:03:16.594 --> 1:03:18.461
(sighs)

1:03:18.463 --> 1:03:19.995
Oh, I really don't know.

1:03:19.997 --> 1:03:22.131
I mean, part of me wishes
you would go first

1:03:22.133 --> 1:03:24.066
so I could launder the sheets.

1:03:24.068 --> 1:03:25.734
There's no time for that,
is there?

1:03:25.736 --> 1:03:28.404
(knocking)

1:03:28.406 --> 1:03:30.172
No.

1:03:30.174 --> 1:03:32.775
It seems not.

1:03:32.777 --> 1:03:34.743
I will go first.

1:03:34.745 --> 1:03:37.413
(knocking continues)

1:03:40.651 --> 1:03:42.418
Gun, please.

1:03:49.660 --> 1:03:51.460
(gasps)

1:03:51.462 --> 1:03:53.262
