1:03:54.632 --> 1:03:57.099
Your last meal?

1:03:57.101 --> 1:03:58.801
(knocking continues)

1:03:58.803 --> 1:04:00.870
Miss Evers.

1:04:03.774 --> 1:04:06.275
(gun clicks)

1:04:07.311 --> 1:04:08.544
(chuckles)

1:04:15.219 --> 1:04:17.286
(knocking continues)

1:04:21.559 --> 1:04:23.259
(choking)

